data.description: PRICE REDUCTION!! Dont' miss your opportunity to see this immaculate 3 bedrooms 2 baths plus  an office home In BARTRAM SPRINGS nestled in a great neighborhood  surrounded by great schools and  shops.This beautiful 3 bedroom 2 baths home has a Beautiful equipped Kitchen over looking the nook area and living room with wood burning fireplace that  overlooks the cozy covered patio, backyard and lake. Tile and laminate throughout the house, carpet in bedrooms. This home is priced to sell!!!! Need 24 hour notice to schedule a showing- see private remarks for showing instructions.
